
To install the lexers to Scintilla, check this webpage:
http://www.scintilla.org/SciTELexer.html

LexerMediaWiki.cxx have been compiled with Scintilla
version 3.0.4, and later versions may not compile properly
or to run bug free.


1. Edit scintilla/include/Scintilla.iface
2. Run scintilla/include/HFacer.py
3. Run scintilla/src/LexGen.py


For cross-compiling Scintilla with MinGW on Linux:

Edit scintilla/win32/makefile
Replace "g++" with "i686-w64-mingw32-g++"
and replace "windres" with "i686-w64-mingw32-windres"


